    <sect3 role="installation">
      <title>Instalao de Sphinxcontrib-applehelp</title>

    <para> Build the module: </para>

<screen><userinput>pip3 wheel -w dist --no-build-isolation --no-deps $PWD</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Agora, como o(a) usurio(a) <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem>:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>pip3 install --no-index --find-links dist --no-cache-dir --no-user sphinxcontrib-applehelp</userinput></screen>

      <para>
        To test the installation, run <command>pytest</command>. Several warnings
may be issued, due to the use of deprecated functions.
      </para>

    </sect3>

